<span id="freeTextContainer17635785876445908874"><br/><br/><br/> What a naive heroine Miss HALA el Wafi is,he defeated her even before the game started &quot;Black suits you” card accompanied with a purple tulip bouquet immediately inflicted her.She didn&apos;t fight at all as the author pictured her ,she has nothing of a so called a “strong personality”.Tulip bouquet after another ,then a meeting from an airport to another,from a city to another and between them she is losing herself respect ,only excuse for her according to ALHAM Mosteghanimi that she didn&apos;t give it</span>
  <span id="freeText17635785876445908874" style="display:none"><br /><br /><br /> What a naive heroine Miss HALA el Wafi is,he defeated her even before the game started "Black suits you” card accompanied with a purple tulip bouquet immediately inflicted her.She didn't fight at all as the author pictured her ,she has nothing of a so called a “strong personality”.Tulip bouquet after another ,then a meeting from an airport to another,from a city to another and between them she is losing herself respect ,only excuse for her according to ALHAM Mosteghanimi that she didn't give it all,but to me failed ,just like a teenage dreamer.<br />She did recognize his true colors,she left him.All end up when he got his own private jet .<br />Result:He is miserable not for losing her but for being a loser thanks to her.His pride is hurt,she heals herself by organizing her biggest minstrel as a revenge. <br /><br />Hala el Wafi has an algerian nationality without an algerian identity<br /></span>
