<ul>
<li class='cover' id='bookCover_7119070'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/7119070"><img alt="أحببتك أكثر مما ينبغي" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1257796264l/7119070._SX98_.jpg" />
